Arthur C. Bass, James J. Penney, and Ramon W. Menzel were named directors of this underground utility inspection and maintenance concern, expanding board membership to eight.
Mr. Bass is president and chief executive officer of Cooper Cos. of Palo Alto, Calif.
Mr. Penney is president of Liberty Capital Group Inc., a Chicago investment banking concern.
Mr. Menzel is president of SOS Service Group Inc., a Brighton, Mich., licensee of IPM's sewer-repair process. 

